{"tid":1900324,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"特西 重出江湖","createTime":"2020-02-27T07:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T10:59:40.000Z","uid":38189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3611c8af8f74b614d915d4fc2369c2b0ab7b13","tid":1900324,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:08:18.000Z","msg":"2020年2月27日 上午7:49<br />\n【星島日報報道】港鐵觀塘線三個車站的月台垃圾桶，在短短半小時內遭人連環縱火，警方正追緝一名懷疑涉案的老翁，案件仍在調查。<br />\n<br />\n事發在昨晚11時許，港鐵九龍灣站月台垃圾桶突然起火，職員發現後迅速將火救熄，事發後約數分鐘，只有一站之隔的彩虹站，月台一個垃圾桶亦冒煙起火焚燒，職員救熄火後，發現地面遺下焚燒過的垃圾。而約10分鐘後，黃大仙站亦發生同類事件，3宗案件均無人受傷，消防接報到場調查，相信均無自然起火原因，認為有可疑，交由警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方在現場拉起封鎖線，正循縱火案方向調查，暫時無人被捕。據悉，警方翻查天眼後，懷疑一名老翁與案件有關，正追查其下落。"},{"pid":"425c572d01b17c2847c7ec2af443266396156466","tid":1900324,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9291a9e64d13d4165302ebb8fcf74358358fb9","tid":1900324,"uid":8968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"咁快變左老翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f195c3b929ece59cd6b162b01c27f49f4de3bdb3","tid":1900324,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fdf57f8999124afd0ca4e1592a38d9712a99f2","tid":1900324,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:15:26.000Z","msg":"放開觀塘區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6fac18f5d9982e8d819a30d437f3b35520b74f","tid":1900324,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a9291a9e64d13d4165302ebb8fcf74358358fb9","tid":1900324,"uid":8968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:09:39.000Z","msg":"咁快變左老翁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTi